    "body" : "<p>To accept both <code>@PathVariable</code> and <code>@RequestParam</code> in the same <code>/user</code> endpoint:</p>\n<pre><code>@GetMapping(path = {&quot;/user&quot;, &quot;/user/{data}&quot;})\npublic void user(@PathVariable(required=false,name=&quot;data&quot;) String data,\n                 @RequestParam(required=false) Map&lt;String,String&gt; qparams) {\n    qparams.forEach((a,b) -&gt; {\n        System.out.println(String.format(&quot;%s -&gt; %s&quot;,a,b));\n    }\n  \n    if (data != null) {\n        System.out.println(data);\n    }\n}\n</code></pre>\n<p>Testing with curl:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>curl 'http://localhost:8080/user/books'</li>\n<li>curl 'http://localhost:8080/user?book=ofdreams&amp;name=nietzsche'</li>\n</ul>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 21338316,
      "reputation" : 91,
      "user_id" : 15709203,
      "user_type" : "registered",
      "profile_image" : "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/AOh14Gik7uar4dgUR-_tLk4SNcUjsHQu0m0bbemCFrd7ww=k-s256",
      "display_name" : "satish gupta",
