    "question_id" : 32201441,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>When using the <code>@GetMapping</code> annotation, you typically use <code>@RequestParam</code> in the request instead of <code>@RequestBody</code>. If you want to use <code>@RequestBody</code>, you should use the <code>@PostMapping</code> annotation in the API method.</p>\n"
