    "body" : "<p>Almost all of these require ANNOTATIONS.</p>\n<p>For a manual/programmatic approach, use the following:</p>\n<pre><code>LinkedHashMap&lt;String, String&gt; post = parsePutParams(IOUtils.toString(request.getInputStream(), StandardCharsets.UTF_8))\n</code></pre>\n"
